This conspicuous regard for martyrs in an early Irish liturgical document is curiouS, because the lrish Church before 1111. 700 had escaped the persecutions of heathendom, and had not produced martyrs. Martyrs, as such, are not invoked in the Litany or Diptychs of the Stowe Missal.
